displayName: Golden City of Dromos, Noble Barssa Residence

Maid who came to work: I won't have any trouble finding work
in this town. Everyone here tries to solve things with
money.

Maid who came to work: I won't have any trouble finding work
in this town. Everyone here tries to solve things with
money.
Mansion Butler: Is there something you need from my master?

Mansion Butler: The master is waiting for you, please come
in.

Mansion Butler: Thanks to everyone, my master's smile has
returned. Thank you very much.

Mansion Butler: Thanks to everyone, my master's smile has
returned. Thank you very much.

Noble Baarsa: Unfortunately, I do not sell medicine to
individuals. I recommend using personal shops and such.
Noble Barusa: I apologize for my rough behavior.
Clea: No problem. Please tell me the details of the request.

Noble Barusa: I was asked by my son Metoki to have [Friend]
deliver something to Beach Lepton.
Noble Barusa: Inside the bag, there are tears of a dragon.

Noble Barusa: If you know, then I'll get straight to the
point. It seems my son wants to take advantage of someone's
kindness and have them deliver something as a courier.

Priestess Sophia: Could you please tell us the reason why
you would make a request despite being aware of it?

Noble Barusa: My son, who has made a fortune in the sale of
medicine, also has talent in concoction, not just sales.

Noble Barusa: I have provided my son with various
educational opportunities in different lands, which is why
he didn't have time to make friends.
Clea: Is it not possible to explain everything?

Noble Barusa: Children often rebel against their parents,
especially when they make their first friends.

Noble Barusa: What I would like to request from all of you
is to prevent my son from making contact with criminals.

Noble Barusa: I want you to expose the criminals to the
guards and make my son realize that he himself has been
involved in crime.
Priestess Sophia: Hehe, it feels quite overprotective.

Noble Barusa: Please laugh at this foolish parent, my
precious heir... I mean, my precious son.

Noble Barusa: The butler should be gathering information on
Beach Lepton, so please join him.
Noble Barusa: Please take care of my son.

Noble Barusa: I believe that my son can grow from this
incident.
